OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening with some
OL,7,Fprolonged spells of late evening
OL,8,Fsunshine. Remaining dry overnight with
OL,9,Fclear spells. Mostly light winds, a
OL,10,Ftouch breezier near the coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FIt will be dry and warm with
OL,13,Flengthy sunny spells for much of the
OL,14,Fday, but sunshine turning somewhat
OL,15,Fhazier as cloud spreads south in the
OL,16,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
