OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FIt
OL,6,Fwill be a mostly dry few days with
OL,7,Fvariable cloud and some warm sunny
OL,8,Fspells, chance of some patchy light
OL,9,Frain on Wednesday morning. Mainly
OL,10,Flight winds.
